snippet.title: ForkJump Short TeaserTrailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist ForkJump: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1425010/ForkJump/

A dark, third-person, open-world exploration game set in a sci-fi environment. Dodge dangers, jumping fork monsters and fork-jump-scares. Master parkour and teleportation to discover secret areas and Forks, delving into the mystery of the Fork obsession and aiming to become the ultimate giga cyborg.

https://www.intety.com
https://www.instagram.com/intetygames/
